I was stupid high for like 3 hours of this bowl so I’m the end I did win!!! 
. 
. 
BONG AND HOSPITALITY- @smokerschoiceredlands 
FLOWER- @budmangardens 
BOWL/FUNNEL- @freshglassco 
. 
. 
CHEERS AND MUCH LOVE Y’ALL

A little got sucked down the neck but most was smoked. 
The main thing was it did the trick because I’m hella lit!! 
CHEERS AND MUCH LOVE Y’ALL 
. 
. 
RIGS- @hemperco 
BANGER- @bearquartz 
FLOWER- @budmangardens 
ROSIN- @burningbushcocal3.0 
. 
.

node.text:
We started off strong but then I broke my @zongglass bong... that didn’t stop us! You gotta finish like you start... STRONG!! 
NEVER QUIT, NEVER GIVE UP! #armstrong 
. 
. 
I’ve been doing these videos with my son @killa_e713 since I started. If you go to my YouTube page and look for the very first video/oldest video... that’s where it all started. Me and my kids have always been inSync and have huge lung capacity made for combos. I couldn’t be more proud of the great hearted adults they have become. 
Love, discipline, respect, congratulate, and cherish every moment with your kids and you’ll create a bond that can never be broken. 
I love you with all my heart @lil.smokie223 and @killa_e713 . Y’all are the greatest kids a dad could ask for.
